# ğŸ’ Naksh Jewels â€” Full Stack Internship Assignment

A full-stack jewelry product listing and cart application built using **React (Vite)** for the frontend and **Node.js + Express** for the backend. The project demonstrates API integration, component architecture, state management, routing, and Dockerized deployment.

