# ğŸš€ Tech Stack

## Frontend

* React (Vite)
* React Router DOM
* Context API (Cart State)
* Axios
* CSS / Inline Styling

## Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* REST API
* dotenv

## DevOps

* Docker
* Docker Compose
* Git & GitHub

