```

Runs on:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

---

# ğŸ³ Docker Setup (Recommended)

Run entire stack:

```
docker compose up --build
```

Services:

| Service  | Port |
| -------- | ---- |
| Frontend | 3000 |
| Backend  | 5000 |

Stop:

```
docker compose down
```

---

# ğŸ›’ Cart Logic

Cart is implemented using React Context API:

* Global cart state
* Add to cart
* Quantity increment/decrement
* Total calculation
* Shared across routes

---

# ğŸ–¼ Image Handling (Pro Approach)

Product images are stored locally:

```
frontend/public/images/
```

Backend returns image paths like:

```
/images/gold-ring.jpg
```

Benefits:

* No external dependency failures
* Faster load
* Stable rendering across environments
* More production-style asset handling

---

